OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772463771
OL,3,CCouncillors 'threatened' with being
OL,4,Csued if they don't pass Birmingham
OL,5,Cbudget
OL,7,FCouncillors in Birmingham have said
OL,8,Fthey have been "threatened" with legal
OL,9,Faction if they fail to pass a budget
OL,10,Fbefore next week's deadline.
OL,12,FIn a strongly-worded letter sent to
OL,13,Fall members after last week's chaotic
OL,14,Fadjourned meeting, the council's City
OL,15,FSolicitor and Monitoring Officer, Tony
OL,16,FCox, spells out what he calls the
OL,17,F"possible consequences" of not setting
OL,18,Fa lawful budget by 11 March.
OL,26,@pD@POUpD@[O]yD@AOUyD@WO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772463771
OL,3,CCouncillors 'threatened' with being
OL,4,Csued if they don't pass Birmingham
OL,5,Cbudget
OL,7,FWhat follows, some councillors say,
OL,8,Freads less like routine legal advice
OL,9,Fand more like a warning shot.
OL,11,FThe letter states there are
OL,12,F"significant consequences for the
OL,13,Fcouncil and for individual members" if
OL,14,Fa budget is not agreed.
OL,16,FIt warns that councillors could be
OL,17,F"personally liable for any losses
OL,18,Fincurred by the council" if it fails
OL,19,Fto set a lawful budget.
OL,26,@tD@AOUuD@cO]yD@AOUzD@XO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772463771
OL,3,CCouncillors 'threatened' with being
OL,4,Csued if they don't pass Birmingham
OL,5,Cbudget
OL,7,FCiting previous court rulings, it says
OL,8,Fthe authority itself could sue its own
OL,9,Fmembers for losses arising from a
OL,10,Fbreach of duty.
OL,12,FCllr Barbara Dring, a Harborne and
OL,13,FQuinton Independent who was deselected
OL,14,Fby Labour last year after supporting
OL,15,Fcomments critical of the council
OL,16,Fonline, said: "I thought it was a
OL,17,Fthreat but I didn't take it seriously
OL,18,Fbecause I know they can't make those
OL,19,Fkind of threats.
OL,26,@xD@OOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772463771
OL,3,CCouncillors 'threatened' with being
OL,4,Csued if they don't pass Birmingham
OL,5,Cbudget
OL,7,F"My conscience would not allow me to
OL,8,Fvote for this budget but they are
OL,9,Ftrying to lean on us to get it through.
OL,11,F"I'm not a nodding dog but I know you
OL,12,Fget punished if you say what you
OL,13,Fthink."
OL,15,FCllr Martin Brookes, also a Harborne
OL,16,Fand Quinton Independent quit Labour
OL,17,Fover budget cuts after the authority
OL,18,Fdeclared effective bankruptcy.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUuD@GO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772463771
OL,3,CCouncillors 'threatened' with being
OL,4,Csued if they don't pass Birmingham
OL,5,Cbudget
OL,7,FHe said he didn't feel threatened by
OL,8,Fthe message but said: "This contains
OL,9,Fthe kind of language which isn't
OL,10,Fuseful in the difficult situation the
OL,11,Fcouncil is in.
OL,13,F"It's quite inappropriate to raise
OL,14,Fthis as an issue and cite legal
OL,15,Fjudgements which are entirely
OL,16,Funconnected.
OL,26,@pD@WOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772463771
OL,3,CCouncillors 'threatened' with being
OL,4,Csued if they don't pass Birmingham
OL,5,Cbudget
OL,7,F"It's the responsibility of the Labour
OL,8,Fgroup to get the budget through the
OL,9,Fcouncil, if they can't they need to go
OL,10,Finto intensive negotiations with other
OL,11,Fparties, until they do it's their
OL,12,Fresponsibility."
OL,14,FCouncillors are also warned that if
OL,15,Fthe council were unable to collect
OL,16,Fcouncil tax because members had
OL,17,F"wilfully failed" to set a budget,
OL,18,Fthey "could potentially be held
OL,19,Fliable" for the losses.
OL,26,@oD@AOUyD@AOUyD@QO]zD@FOU{D@GO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772463771
OL,3,CCouncillors 'threatened' with being
OL,4,Csued if they don't pass Birmingham
OL,5,Cbudget
OL,7,FA Birmingham City Council spokesperson
OL,8,Fsaid: "The council has a legal
OL,9,Fobligation to pass its budget for the
OL,10,Fcoming financial year by 11 March,
OL,11,Fwhich is the statutory deadline to set
OL,12,Fcouncil tax levels.
OL,14,F"As such all members need to be clear
OL,15,Fabout their responsibility in setting
OL,16,Fa lawful budget. This is as set out in
OL,17,Fthe budget report to council."
OL,26,@pD@GOUyD@^O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772463771
OL,3,CCouncillors 'threatened' with being
OL,4,Csued if they don't pass Birmingham
OL,5,Cbudget
OL,7,FThe row comes at a sensitive time for
OL,8,FBirmingham City Council, which has
OL,9,Fbeen under the oversight of government-
OL,10,Fappointed commissioners since 2023
OL,11,Fafter effectively declaring itself
OL,12,Fbankrupt, amid a financial crisis
OL,13,Flinked to equal pay liabilities and a
OL,14,Fbotched IT system.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772463771
OL,3,CCouncillors 'threatened' with being
OL,4,Csued if they don't pass Birmingham
OL,5,Cbudget
OL,7,FLast month, leaders said the authority
OL,8,Fwas no longer effectively bankrupt and
OL,9,Funveiled plans for what they described
OL,10,Fas a balanced 2026-27 budget,
OL,11,Fincluding #130m of investment in
OL,12,Fservices, the first balanced budget in
OL,13,Fthree years.
OL,15,FBut a full council meeting to approve
OL,16,Fthe plans ended without a resolution
OL,17,Fafter defections and resignations
OL,18,Freduced Labour's majority on the 101-
OL,19,Fmember authority. Some councillors
OL,20,Fwere not in attendance.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772463771
OL,3,CCouncillors 'threatened' with being
OL,4,Csued if they don't pass Birmingham
OL,5,Cbudget
OL,7,FBrookes added: "This situation is
OL,8,Fentirely of Labour's own making, they
OL,9,Fhad a majority of 29 over all other
OL,10,Fparties combined and they frittered
OL,11,Fthat away with de-selection and
OL,12,Fremovals.
OL,14,F"Now they're in a situation where they
OL,15,Fcan barely get the budget through."
OL,26,@oD@POUvD@AOUwD@cO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772463771
OL,3,CCouncillors 'threatened' with being
OL,4,Csued if they don't pass Birmingham
OL,5,Cbudget
OL,7,FLocal Conservatives have also weighed
OL,8,Fin. Group leader Cllr Robert Alden
OL,9,Fsaid: "While we understand the legal
OL,10,Fdepartment have a job to do, every
OL,11,Fcouncillor must also remember they
OL,12,Fcannot be made to vote for a budget
OL,13,Fthey believe will harm the city.
OL,15,F"No one can make councillors vote for
OL,16,FLabour's double whammy of higher taxes
OL,17,Ffor fewer services, anyone who does
OL,18,Fvote for it is choosing to".
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772463771
OL,3,CCouncillors 'threatened' with being
OL,4,Csued if they don't pass Birmingham
OL,5,Cbudget
OL,7,FConservaitve Cllr Ewan Mackey said:
OL,8,F"No amount of intimidation will stop
OL,9,Fthe opposition standing up for
OL,10,Fresidents and voting against the
OL,11,FLabour double whammy budget today".
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/12
